      "content": "i mean i get the definitions, but that feels a bit like a textbook answer. you're being pretty vague. if you look at how it actually plays out—like in universities or big companies—it seems like it's moving more towards the censorship side where people are afraid to say anything \"wrong.\" don't you think that's a more significant problem than the social justice part?",
